from test: 8 Unless otherwise specified, the steel surface for SKP and LEIS measurements was grinded using silicon carbide paper down to SiC #1000, degreased in ethanol, rinsed in deionized water and stored in dry air. A constant load cell equipped with load sensor was used to apply tensile load in the range of 200–650 MPa.20
from Soup: 8 Unless otherwise specified, the steel surface for SKP and LEIS measurements was grinded using silicon carbide paper down to SiC #1000, degreased in ethanol, rinsed in deionized water and stored in dry air. A constant load cell equipped with load sensor was used to apply tensile load in the range of 200–650 MPa. 20
