from test: 11 A potentiostat (Gamry, Reference 600) was used for pre-treating steel in an aqueous buffer electrolyte 0.075 M Na2B4O7 10 H2O / 0.015 M B(OH)3 (pH = 9.2). A 3-electrode cell was used including a Pt wire counter-electrode and Ag/AgCl saturated electrode as a reference.
