from test: 33 Figure 10b shows the potential distribution for steel after an anodic polarization of 0.4 V/SHE. Some locations inside the notch exhibited increased Volta potential and some of them show very low potentials. The potential contrast between strained and non-strained area increased to 500 mV. Thus SKP visualizes the areas with residual stress which have low ability to passivate the surface.
